sentences: Chu Eun-yul (born July 11, 1968), better known as Chu Ga-yeoul, is a South Korean folk-pop singer and songwriter.
Chu auditioned at SM in 2001 and received a standing ovation by Lee Soo Man.

He signed with them that year.

On the radio show Ahn SeonYoung's Radio Is Good on May 19, Chu Ga Yeol said  "Among the hoobaes of Super Junior that I taught how to play the guitar, Sungmin is the one who learnt to play well right away.
Sungmin had previously said to Chu "If there are chances, I want to play the guitar on stage with you."
The two would later perform a cover of "Just The Two Of Us" at SMTown Live '08 and Chu Ga Yeol's X-Mas Concert.
